PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-551 of April 11, 1997 which appointed ALEX G. BALOGH as a director of the Board of Directors of the Cape Breton Development Corporation, by adding the words "in the place of Allister Angus Mackenzie whose term has expired".
